dc_title_s: State of New Jersey Board of Commerce and Navigation Map showing proposed pierhead and bulkhead line on Barnegat Bay southwest from Bay Head-Manasquan Canal
dc_description_s: A blueprint with accompanying tracing showing a proposed pierhead and bulkhead line along Barnegat Bay. The bulkhead and pierhead lines are marked in red on the tracing. It also includes some information on water depth and property lots along the coast.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
